{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be corporate and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artist Portfolio - [Artist Name]</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #B71C1C; /* Deep Red */\n            --secondary-color: #E57373; /* Lighter Red/Pink */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FAFAFA;\n            --nav-background: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #212121;\n            --footer-text-color: #eeeeee;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header .tagline {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            color: #f5f5f5;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--nav-background);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 100;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item {\n            background-color: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item-details {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item-details h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item-details p {\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        #about .container {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        #about .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #about .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        #about .about-text h2 {\n            text-align: left;\n            margin-left: 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact .container {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #D32F2F; /* Darker Red */\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--footer-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n            <p class=\"tagline\">Contemporary Art & Vision</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Explore the Canvas</h2>\n            <p>Discover a curated collection of works that blend bold expression with refined technique.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/B71C1C/ffffff?text=Artwork+1\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-details\">\n                        <h3>Crimson Abstract</h3>\n                        <p>An exploration of texture and emotion, using acrylics on canvas.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/E57373/ffffff?text=Artwork+2\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-details\">\n                        <h3>Urban Sunrise</h3>\n                        <p>Capturing the fleeting light of dawn in a cityscape, oil on board.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/D32F2F/ffffff?text=Artwork+3\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-details\">\n                        <h3>Geometric Harmony</h3>\n                        <p>A study in form and color, digital painting.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/B71C1C/ffffff?text=Artwork+4\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-details\">\n                        <h3>Whispers of Nature</h3>\n                        <p>Mixed media, inspired by natural landscapes.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"about-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x400/333333/ffffff?text=Artist+Photo\" alt=\"Artist Photo\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <h2>About the Artist</h2>\n                <p>With a passion for expressive and impactful art, [Artist Name] creates pieces that resonate with viewers on a deep level. Specializing in [mention primary medium/style, e.g., abstract expressionism, contemporary realism], the artist draws inspiration from [mention sources of inspiration, e.g., urban environments, natural forms, human emotion]. Each artwork is a journey, meticulously crafted to evoke thought and feeling.</p>\n                <p>Based in [City, State], [Artist Name]'s work has been featured in [mention galleries or exhibitions, if applicable] and is collected by patrons worldwide.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>For inquiries about commissions, acquisitions, or collaborations, please use the form below.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Designed with passion by <a href=\"#\">[Your Name/Company]</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}